{"tid":1309910,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"HELP!!!! hard disk 壞左求救","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T19:34:55.000Z","uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6f799fd6b35a06a0849d38e3d69717da265cb6","tid":1309910,"uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:58:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思咁多位，小妹係電腦白痴黎，頭先用緊個外置hard disk，佢跟開條usb線係雙頭嘅，頭先我好似插左另外一邊頭(平時冇用開)，然後個hard disk 高噠噠噠左3聲。我都估到即刻瀨野嫁，就即刻掹線等佢cool down再插過。<br />\n然後我部mac pro就crush左唔郁，冇耐就彈左以下圖片出黎:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NGxfhN2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNGxfhN2.png&h=eb50ea24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我排過文好多人都係用Windows，同埋完全冇圖唔知佢地情況係點，睇人地師兄介紹嗰啲software 就更加唔敢試，有冇師兄可以建議下點做。我已經即刻問我朋友借左部mac pro，同埋買埋新hard disk，麻煩大家俾啲意見，搵人整都可以，只要介紹係信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e505a862a3f66d0829f4636532a7ce6bc13c59","tid":1309910,"uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ae627ae755d98feddcd19eedc67d2afef79ddb1","tid":1309910,"uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"我知可能好小事 但hard disk壞左真係好心慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb3f9def2ebf2253336d398b8e7defc4add8662","tid":1309910,"uid":270613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec02ef1ffc4d80e8a2610cb49223614c0ecb2f56","tid":1309910,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:09:50.000Z","msg":"拎去apple睇下"},{"pid":"c34319d5dfc90a7ae87ab0374fe1cb1141404e5d","tid":1309910,"uid":169498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:34:55.000Z","msg":"Push 同樣情況 ，跪地求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}